               <msContents>
                  <summary>The Ms. contains the following texts: 
 I) Mǝʿrāf, Common of the
                     Office (fols. 1rv, 6ra-36vb), incomplete
 I-1) Wāzemā, The Office of Vigils
                     (fols. 1rv, 6ra-10rb)
 I-2) Kǝśtat za-ʾaryām, The festive Office (fols.
                     10va-19vb l.10)
 I-3) Mawaddǝs, The Sunday Office (fols. 19vb
                     l.11-36vb).
 II) Mawāśǝʾt, Antiphonary for feasts and funeral service
                     [contains fragments of Dǝggʷā, Antiphonary](fols. 2ra-5vb, 37rv),
                     incomplete.</summary>
